Date: Tue, 4 Nov 2025 09:53:23 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:HOSTAPD: Unify WFA capability IE for SCS
and DSCP policy

Introduce a single Wi‑Fi Alliance capability element to advertise
SCS and DSCP policy capabilities, and use it across beacon, probe
response, and association response paths.

Patch-dependency: r90-02-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-HOSTAPD-Add-DSCP-Capability-advert.patch
Signed-off-by: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
